==English==

=== Preposition ===
'''thru'''
# ''(Informal)'' Simplified variant of [[through]].
#: ''We'll be on vacation '''thru''' the end of July''

==== Usage Note ====
As an informal variant of ''through'', ''thru'' is generally only used as a preposition (e.g., ''Monday ''thru'' Friday''), and rarely as an adjective or adverb (e.g., ''I'm ''thru'' with vacuuming!'').  Additionally, it is subject to correction, and it is rarely used in formal situations, except in cases where extreme brevity is needed, such as roadway signage.

